dialogueTree.title: Barry the Butcher: "“How am I supposed to get across no..."
dialogueTree.english: “How am I supposed to get across now?"
dialogueTree.polish: „I jak mam teraz przejść na drugą stronę?”
dialogueTree.belarusian: «І як мне цяпер перайсці на другі бок?»

dialogueTree.title: Barry the Butcher: ""Can't wait till Wednesday, I got m..."
dialogueTree.english: "Can't wait till Wednesday, I got meat to sell."
dialogueTree.polish: „Nie mogę czekać aż do środy – mam mięso do sprzedania”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Я не магу чакаць да серады — у мяне мяса на продаж».

dialogueTree.title: Barry the Butcher: ""If I ever get my hands on the idio..."
dialogueTree.english: "If I ever get my hands on the idiot who broke that sign..."
dialogueTree.polish: „Gdybym dorwał tego idiotę, który przewrócił tę tablicę reklamową...”
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Каб я злавіў таго ідыёта, які перакуліў гэты рэкламны шчыт...»
